Rudimentary multi-database configuration.

> alembic revision -m "Add a column"

add code to upgrade()

> alembic upgrade head

[Reference](https://alembic.zzzcomputing.com/en/latest/tutorial.html#the-migration-environment)

also, [flask-migrate](https://github.com/miguelgrinberg/Flask-Migrate) seems awesome!

